    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>tofu </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper, then cut into strips</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>tofu strips</strong></p><p>Combine your<strong> cornflour </strong>with the<strong> remaining ground smoked paprika </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>on a plate</p><p>Press the <strong>marinated tofu strips</strong> into the<strong> spiced flour</strong>, turning a couple of times until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
