    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the tofu is cooking, finely dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomato</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the bowl of quick-pickled shallot and mix to combine<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p>",
