    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 1-2 min, or until warmed through</p><p>Meanwhile, return the <strong>spiced corn </strong>to a medium heat to warm through, then stir through<strong> half</strong> your <strong>cultured</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) – this is your <strong>creamy corn</strong></p>",
